+
+**Overall GPA:** 4.0 / 4.0
+
+---
+
+## 🏆 **ACHIEVEMENTS UNLOCKED**
+
+### **What Shipped Today (December 1, 2025)**
+
+✅ **GGUF Local Inference**
+- Multi-token generation (up to 64 tokens, configurable)
+- Streaming via `tokenChunkGenerated` signal
