+## 🎯 **IMMEDIATE "NEXT CLASS" ELECTIVES**
+### (Pick any 1-2 weekends)
+
+### **Elective 1: Real Transformer Layers**
+**Effort:** 1 weekend | **Impact:** 🔥🔥🔥🔥🔥
